Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Fields
  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Fields 
    Field and Description
    uws.job.UWSJob.dateFormat
    Replaced by ISO8601Format.
    uws.job.UWSJob.DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT
    Replaced by ISO8601Format.
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    adql.parser.ADQLQueryFactory.createColRef(IdentifierItems)
    since 1.4 ; Former version's mistake: a GROUP BY item is either a regular/delimited column name or an integer, not a qualified column name ; Replaced by #createColRef(IdentifierItem) ; This function is no longer used by ADQLParser.
    adql.parser.ADQLQueryFactory.createOrder(IdentifierItems, boolean)
    since 1.4 ; Former version's mistake: an ORDER BY item is either a regular/delimited column name or an integer, not a qualified column name ; Replaced by #createOrder(IdentifierItem, boolean) ; This function is no longer used by ADQLParser.
    adql.parser.ADQLQueryFactory.createOrder(int, boolean, TextPosition)
    since 1.4 ; Replaced by ADQLQueryFactory.createOrder(int, boolean)
    adql.parser.SimpleCharStream.getColumn()
    uws.job.parameters.ExecutionDurationController.getDefaultExecutionDuration()
    This function is completely equivalent to ExecutionDurationController.getDefault().
    adql.parser.SimpleCharStream.getLine()
    tap.metadata.TAPTable.getName()
    Does not do anything special: just call TAPTable.getADQLName().
    tap.metadata.TAPSchema.getName()
    Does not do anything special: just call TAPSchema.getADQLName().
    tap.metadata.TAPColumn.getName()
    Does not do anything special: just call TAPColumn.getADQLName().
    tap.resource.TAP.getTAPResources()
    The name of this function has been normalized. So now, you should use TAP.getResources() which is doing exactly the same thing.
